snippet.title: AMBER HEARD STOLE FROM CHARITY. A Story You Won’t See In The News... Armie Hammer's DM's.
snippet.description:
Greetings friends!

In this episode, we discuss the fact that Amber Heard has yet to donate any of the 7 million dollars she received in her divorce settlement to Johnny Depp. We also touch on Armie Hammer's interesting way of communicating through DM's. 

If you enjoyed please COMMENT, LIKE, & SUBSCRIBE.
